Class Tasklist

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onfleet.demo.homework.collection.Tasklist

  • public final class Tasklist
extends Object
    Specifies a task-list for a given Driver, which contains Task objects currently assigned to that Driver.

      • costToAssignTask

        public float costToAssignTask(Task task)
        Query this Driver's task-list about how difficult it would be to assign it a given Task. "Cost" in this context is defined by the following algorithm: 
        summedDistanceOfTasks
        .
        Parameters:
        task - Subject Task to query this task-list for.
        Returns:
        Estimated cost, as a floating point value, or 
        0.0
        if this would be this Driver's first assigned task, and thus the cost would essentially be the distance of the task itself.
        Since:
        1.0
